OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combating bullying
OL,6,FJersey's Civil Service has made "good
OL,7,Fprogress" on combating harassment and
OL,8,Fbullying with further space for
OL,9,Fimprovement, according to a new report.
OL,11,FUK consulting company HR Lounge
OL,12,Fpublished its 2025 report that found
OL,13,Fthe States' public bodies had
OL,14,Fimproved, following a previously
OL,15,Fdamning report from 2018.
OL,17,FThat report cited that the States had
OL,18,F"a level of bullying and harassment
OL,19,Fcomplaints that is significant".
