OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combating bullying
OL,6,FWhile the new report highlights some
OL,7,Ffurther improvements, it adds that
OL,8,Faspects of the civil service's work to
OL,9,Fimprove their services were better
OL,10,Fthan "what other like-minded employers
OL,11,Foffer".
OL,13,FIn his first interview since taking on
OL,14,Fthe Civil Service CEO role, Dr Andrew
OL,15,FMcLaughlin says the bullying was
OL,16,F"certainly something I was aware of"
OL,17,Fbut added that the situation has
OL,18,Fimproved.
