OL,4,Cprogress' on combating bullying
OL,6,FHe explains: "I think we've just had a
OL,7,Fpiece done (late last year) which
OL,8,Fshows that aspect of public services
OL,9,Fis improving significantly.
OL,11,F"It's not been a big feature of my
OL,12,Ftime in the public service.
OL,14,F"What I observe most every day is just
OL,15,Fpublic servants getting on with their
OL,16,Fjob, trying to improve the life of
OL,17,Fislanders.
