OL,3,CJersey Civil Service making 'good
OL,4,Cprogress' on combating bullying
OL,6,F"The public service has got a very
OL,7,Fclear set of values and it's got a
OL,8,Fzero tolerance of poor behaviour in
OL,9,Fgeneral - particularly when it comes
OL,10,Fto poor behaviour in the form of
OL,11,Fbullying and it just won't be
OL,12,Ftolerated.
OL,14,F"I think we've shown over the past
OL,15,Fcouple of years an improving trend."
OL,17,FDr Andrew McLaughlin became the
OL,18,Finterim head of the island's civil
OL,19,Fservice in September 2023 following
OL,20,Fthe resignation of Suzanne Wiley.
