OL,6,FThe CEO was then given a new contract
OL,7,Ffrom 1 July 2024 with a six-month
OL,8,Freview period to continue in the
OL,9,Fposition.
OL,11,FDr McLauglin said "I've just been
OL,12,Fblessed to have had such a varied
OL,13,Fcareer.
OL,15,F"All I do and I think every leader is
OL,16,Fthe same is trying to ensure that when
OL,17,FI leave the place, it's in better
OL,18,Fshape than when I found it. And
OL,19,Fthere's a couple of people wo can do
OL,20,Fthe job after I'm gone."
